{"meta":{"authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}],"title":"","dates":{"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:23 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:23 UTC"}},"nodes":[{"index":0,"parent_index":-1,"body":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">In Spoken Tibetan, compound verbs are more common than simple verbs (verbs comprising only one syllable). For the most part, compound verbs consist of a noun and a &ldquo;verbalizer.&rdquo; Verbalizers (<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱ་ཚིག་སྟོང་པ་</span>) are verbs that do not convey a specific meaning, or else mean &ldquo;to do&rdquo; in a general sense. Compound verbs of this sort generally comprise two or three syllables, but some contain up to five.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The three basic verbalizers are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་</span> / <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གནང་</span> (H) &ldquo;To do,&rdquo; &ldquo;to act&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་</span> / <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བསྐྱོན་</span> (H) &ldquo;To make&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་</span> / <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་གནང་</span> (H) &ldquo;To send,&rdquo; &ldquo;to do&rdquo;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Other verbalizers (some of them used only rarely) include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཟོ་</span> &ldquo;To make&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཞུ་</span> (H) &ldquo;To say,&rdquo; &ldquo;to take&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཞེས་</span> &ldquo;To take&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བསླངས་</span> &ldquo;To lift&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལང་</span> &ldquo;To get up&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འགྲོ་</span> &ldquo;To go&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཤོར་</span> &ldquo;To let go&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཐེབས་</span> &ldquo;To be caught,&rdquo; &ldquo;to be hit&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འཁོར་</span> &ldquo;To circulate&rdquo;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The choice of verbalizer is determined partly by whether the verb is volitional or non-volitional. The verbalizers <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཤོར་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འགྲོ་</span>, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལང་</span>, and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཐེབས་</span> are used in the formation of non-volitional verbs. Following is a chart of some common volitional and non-volitional forms.</p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མགོ་སྐོར་བཏང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To deceive&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མགོ་འཁོར་ཐེབས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To be deceived&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁོང་ཁྲོ་བསླང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To make angry&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁོང་ཁྲོ་ལང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To get angry&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཡར་རྒྱས་བཏང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To improve&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཡར་རྒྱས་འགྲོ་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To be improved&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མེ་མདའ་རྒྱག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To shoot&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མེ་མདའ་ཐེབས་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To be hit (by a bullet)&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མིག་ཆུ་བཏང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To shed tears&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མིག་ཆུ་ཤོར་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To burst into tears&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྟུག་དྲི་བཏང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To fart (intentionally)&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྟུག་དྲི་ཤོར་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To fart (accidentally)&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཅིན་པ་བཏང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To urinate (intentionally)</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཅིན་པ་ཤོར་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To wet oneself &ldquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བསམ་བློ་བཏང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To ponder&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བསམ་བློ་འཁོར་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To have an idea&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐྱུག་པ་སྐྱུག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To (make oneself) vomit&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐྱུག་པ་ཤོར་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To vomit&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The honorifics of compound verbs are formed by putting both the verbalizer and the preceding noun in the honorific.</p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆང་ས་རྒྱག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To marry&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁྲུང་ས་བསྐྱོན་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To marry&rdquo; (H)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལས་ཀ་བྱེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To work&rdquo;</p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཕྱག་ལས་གནང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"414\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To work&rdquo; (H)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Compound verbs retain a certain syntactic flexibility: the noun can be separated from the verbalizer by an adverb or a negation, and may also be marked by a complement:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བསམ་བློ་མང་པོ་བཏང་དགོས་རེད།</span> &ldquo;(We) have to give it a lot of thought.&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བུ་མོས་གཞས་སྙན་པོ་ཅིག་བཏང་སོང་།</span> &ldquo;The girl sang a lovely song.&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཟབ་གཟབ་མ་བྱས་ན་ཉེན་ཁ་འདུག</span> &ldquo;If you&rsquo;re not careful, it&rsquo;s risky.&rdquo;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">The semantics of a verb offer no clue to the verbalizer that should be used. As a general rule, compound verbs take only one verbalizer.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལས་ཀ་བྱེད་</span> &ldquo;To work&rdquo; (but not *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལས་ཀ་བཏང་</span> or *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལས་ཀ་རྒྱག་</span>)</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆང་ས་རྒྱག་</span> &ldquo;To marry&rdquo; (but not *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆང་ས་བྱེད་</span> or *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆང་ས་བཏང་</span>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">In certain cases, however, there is a choice of which verbalizer may be used:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བེད་སྤྱོད་བཏང་</span> or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བེད་སྤྱོད་བྱེད་</span> &ldquo;To use&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འགུལ་སྐྱོད་བརྒྱབ་</span> or <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འགུལ་སྐྱོད་བྱེད་</span> &ldquo;To move&rdquo; </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">In some exceptional instances, different verbalizers may be used but the overall meaning is different in each case.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐད་བཏང་</span> &ldquo;To call,&rdquo; but <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐད་རྒྱག་</span> &ldquo;To shout&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མེ་རྒྱག་</span> &ldquo;To set fire,&rdquo; but <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མེ་བཏང་</span> &ldquo;To light,&rdquo; &ldquo;to make a fire&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལན་རྒྱག་</span> &ldquo;To reply,&rdquo; but <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལན་བཏང་</span> &ldquo;To send a message&rdquo;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Like all verbs, verbalizers must be followed by auxiliaries. Here is a list of the &ldquo;conjugations&rdquo; (in all the tense-aspects and moods) of the most common auxiliaries. Knowing all these forms will enable you to conjugate most verbs in Standard Tibetan.</p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་(གཏོང་)གི་ཡིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་གི་ཡིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་གི་ཡིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་(གཏོང་)གི་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་གི་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་གི་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་(གཏོང་)གི་ཡོད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་གི་ཡོད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་གི་ཡོད་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་(གཏོང་)གི་འདུག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་གི་འདུག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་ཀྱི་འདུག་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་(གཏོང་)གི་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་གི་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་ཀྱི་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་པ་ཡིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱབ་པ་ཡིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱས་པ་ཡིན་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་བྱུང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱབ་བྱུང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱས་བྱུང་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་སོང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱབ་སོང་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱས་སོང་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་པ་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱབ་པ་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱས་པ་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་ཡོད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱབ་ཡོད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱས་ཡོད་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་བཞག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱབ་བཞག་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱས་བཞག་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱབ་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"195\" valign=\"top\">\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱས་ཡོད་རེད་</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Note: The egophoric auxiliaries and the perfect auxiliaries are not compatible with all verbs. For example, for a verb such as <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐད་བཏང་</span> &ldquo;to call,&rdquo; depending on context it is possible to use either the intentional auxiliary or the receptive auxiliary: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐད་བཏང་པ་ཡིན།</span> &ldquo;I called,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐད་བཏང་བྱུང་།</span> &ldquo;I was called (by someone).&rdquo; On the other hand, for a non-volitional verb such as <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྨི་ལམ་བཏང་</span> &ldquo;to dream,&rdquo; the intentional auxiliary is incorrect *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྨི་ལམ་བཏང་པ་ཡིན།</span> and instead the receptive auxiliary must be used <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྨི་ལམ་བཏང་བྱུང་།</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Some verbs can take a complement in the form of a direct or an indirect object, whereas others cannot. The verbalizer gives no indication as to whether a verb is &ldquo;transitive&rdquo; or &ldquo;intransitive.&rdquo; The following verbs all take an object:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁོས་(རྒྱ་སྐད་)སློབ་སྦྱོང་བྱས་པ་རེད།</span> &ldquo;He studied (Chinese).&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁོས་(གློག་ལས་འཁྲུལ་འཁོར་)བེད་སྤྱོད་བྱས་པ་རེད།</span> &ldquo;He used (the computer).&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དགེ་རྒན་གྱིས་(སློབ་མ་)སྐད་བཏང་སོང་།</span> &ldquo;The teacher called (the student).&rdquo; </li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ང་ལ་(ཁྱེད་རང་)རྨི་ལམ་བཏང་བྱུང་།</span> &ldquo;I dreamed (about you).&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དགེ་རྒན་གྱིས་(གནས་ཚུལ་)ངོ་སྤྲོད་ཞུས་སོང་།</span> &ldquo;The teacher presented (the situation).&rdquo;</li>\n<li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁོང་གིས་(ཆོས་)ཉམས་ལེན་ཞེ་པོ་ཅིག་བྱེད་ཀྱི་འདུག་ག</span> &ldquo;He practices (the Dharma) a lot!&rdquo; </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Unlike the verb &ldquo;to study,&rdquo; the verb &ldquo;to work&rdquo; is not transitive, and we can&rsquo;t say: *<span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁོས་(ཤིང་)ལས་ཀ་བྱས་པ་རེད།</span> &ldquo;He worked the wood.&rdquo;</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><em>Note</em>: Several &ldquo;intransitive&rdquo; compound verbs take an ergative construction, whereas in the case of &ldquo;simple&rdquo; verbs this construction occurs only with transitive verbs. This may be explained by the fact that the noun that precedes the verbalizer can be assimilated to an &ldquo;internal&rdquo; object. In other words, the verbalizer acts as if it were an autonomous transitive verb.</p>\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མགོ་སྐོར་བཏང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To deceive&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མགོ་འཁོར་ཐེབས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To be deceived&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁོང་ཁྲོ་བསླང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To make angry&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁོང་ཁྲོ་ལང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To get angry&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཡར་རྒྱས་བཏང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To improve&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཡར་རྒྱས་འགྲོ་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To be improved&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མེ་མདའ་རྒྱག་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To shoot&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མེ་མདའ་ཐེབས་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To be hit (by a bullet)&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མིག་ཆུ་བཏང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To shed tears&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མིག་ཆུ་ཤོར་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To burst into tears&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྟུག་དྲི་བཏང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To fart (intentionally)&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྟུག་དྲི་ཤོར་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To fart (accidentally)&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཅིན་པ་བཏང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To urinate (intentionally)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཅིན་པ་ཤོར་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To wet oneself &ldquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བསམ་བློ་བཏང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To ponder&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བསམ་བློ་འཁོར་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To have an idea&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐྱུག་པ་སྐྱུག་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To (make oneself) vomit&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྐྱུག་པ་ཤོར་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To vomit&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆང་ས་རྒྱག་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To marry&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁྲུང་ས་བསྐྱོན་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To marry&rdquo; (H)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལས་ཀ་བྱེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To work&rdquo;</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཕྱག་ལས་གནང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">&ldquo;To work&rdquo; (H)</p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\">Verbalizer <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་(གཏོང་)གི་ཡིན་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་གི་ཡིན་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་གི་ཡིན་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཏང་(གཏོང་)གི་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྒྱག་གི་རེད་</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེད་གི་རེད་</sp